Feature: Pin Columns
Scenario: To Validate PIN Columns - Pin Left  
    Given Open Browser
    And Navigate Account information section	
	And User Nagivate to summary tab
	And Click on Menu of desired column 
	When User Click on Pin Column
	Then User Select Pin Left
	Then Validate Selected Column should pin to Left side 
	And Close Browser 

Scenario: To Validate PIN Columns - Pin Right  
    Given Open Browser
    And Navigate Account information section	
	And User Nagivate to summary tab
	And Click on Menu of desired column 
	When User Click on Pin Column
	Then User Select Pin Right 
	Then Validate Selected Column should pin to Right side 
	And Close Browser 
	
Scenario: To Validate PIN Columns - No Pin  
    Given Open Browser
    And Navigate Account information section	
	And User Nagivate to summary tab
	And Click on Menu of desired column 
	When User Click on Pin Column
	Then User Select No Pin 
	Then Validate Selected Column should in same position 
	And Close Browser 